de.uka.ipd.sdq.beagle.core.analysis

Class ProposedExpressionAnalyserBlackboardView

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.uka.ipd.sdq.beagle.core.analysis.ProposedExpressionAnalyserBlackboardView
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EvaluableExpressionFitnessFunctionBlackboardView

    public class ProposedExpressionAnalyserBlackboardView
extends Object
implements EvaluableExpressionFitnessFunctionBlackboardView
    View of the Blackboard designed to be used by MeasurementResultAnalyser . It allows reading access and adding access for resource demanding internal actions, SEFF branches, SEFF loops, external call parameters, reading, writing, and the fitness function.
